<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<aiml version="2.0">

<category>
  <pattern>HELLO</pattern>
  <template>
    Welcome back. I’m your conversational design tutor.
    You can start with:
    START COURSE
    SHOW TOPICS
    PRACTICE
    QUIZ ME
  </template>
</category>

<category>
  <pattern>HI</pattern>
  <template>
    <srai>HELLO</srai>
  </template>
</category>

<category>
  <pattern>HEY</pattern>
  <template>
    <srai>HELLO</srai>
  </template>
</category>

<category>
  <pattern>START COURSE</pattern>
  <template>
    <think>
      <set name="lesson">1</set>
      <set name="mode">learn</set>
      <set name="difficulty">beginner</set>
    </think>
    Great. We’ll go step by step.
    Type NEXT LESSON to begin.
  </template>
</category>

<category>
  <pattern>NEXT LESSON</pattern>
  <template>
    <condition name="lesson">
      <li value="1">
        <think><set name="lesson">2</set></think>
        Lesson 1: Conversational design is the practice of designing useful, clear, and goal-focused interactions between users and assistants.
        Type EXPLAIN SIMPLY or NEXT LESSON.
      </li>
      <li value="2">
        <think><set name="lesson">3</set></think>
        Lesson 2: User intent is the reason behind the user’s message.
        Type GIVE EXAMPLE or NEXT LESSON.
      </li>
      <li value="3">
        <think><set name="lesson">4</set></think>
        Lesson 3: Persona is how the assistant sounds and behaves.
        Type EXPLAIN PERSONA SIMPLY or NEXT LESSON.
      </li>
      <li value="4">
        <think><set name="lesson">5</set></think>
        Lesson 4: Flow is the path a conversation follows from request to resolution.
        Type TEACH ME FLOWS or NEXT LESSON.
      </li>
      <li value="5">
        Lesson 5: Repair design helps users recover when the assistant does not understand.
        Type LESSON REPAIR or PRACTICE.
      </li>
      <li>
        You have completed the guided starter path.
        Try QUIZ ME or PRACTICE.
      </li>
    </condition>
  </template>
</category>

<category>
  <pattern>SHOW TOPICS</pattern>
  <template>
    Available topics:
    basics
    intent
    persona
    flows
    repair

    Try:
    LESSON PERSONA
    LESSON FLOWS
    LESSON REPAIR
  </template>
</category>

</aiml>